# Web System

Project COVID-19.
=============

Specification:
-------------

* Server HTTP: Apache 2.4
* SGDB: PostgreSQL 10

Front-End:
* [AngularJS 8](https://angular.io/)

Back-End:
* Venv
* Python 3.6.8

Infer:
* Venv
* Python 3.6.9

Clara:
* Venv
* Python 3.6.9

Server:
-------------
| Server| Service       | File                              | Pip List        |
|-------|-------------- | --------------------------------- | --------------- |
| 1     | Front-End     | /frontend/*                       | None            |
| 1     | Back-End      | /backend/BackEnd/api.py           | pip_backend.txt |
| 2     | Infer         | /backend/Infer/app.py             | pip_infer.txt   |
| 3     | Clara Infer   | /backend/Clara Infer/app_clara.py | pip_infer.txt   |

# API - Back-End System

## Dashboard Confirmed Case Total

```
GET /api/dashboard/confirmed/total_cases/?country=<country>&state=<state>
```
### Example
country = Brazil & state = Bahia
country = Angola & state = null

### Test
```
curl -i \
-X GET \
https://covid19.fieb.org.br:9050/api/dashboard/confirmed/total_cases/?country=Brazil&state=Bahia

curl -i \
-X GET \
https://covid19.fieb.org.br:9050/api/dashboard/confirmed/total_cases/?country=Angola&state=null
```

```
GET api/dashboard/invoices/quantity/?state=<state>
```

## Dashboard Restrictive

```
GET api/dashboard/restrictive/?country=<country>
```
### Example
country = Brazil
country = Angola

### Test
```
curl -i \
-X GET \
https://covid19.fieb.org.br:9050/api/dashboard/restrictive/?country=Brazil
```
